{"userId":"mrnXW7vWxnscA7Qp","username":"s","title":" That Time I Got Reincarnated as a Slime - Episode 57 (S3E09) [English Sub]","description":"Episode 57：Seven Days Clergy's Conspiracy\nEpisode Summary：\nWhile Rimuru and Hinata were fighting to the death in Tempest, a man was conspiring behind the scenes in Maris, the capital city of Falmuth. The man's name was Damrada. He noticed the existence of a Primal Demon among the enemy forces and pulled some strings before he disappeared. Meanwhile,  the demon in question, Diablo, descends in front of his enemy, King Edward. In the presence of reports from various nations, he warns the king to make peace with Youm, but the king refuses, as he has the Three Battlesages on his side. In response, Diablo ruthlessly instills fear in all his enemies.","youtubeUrl":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8HkL25ulB2g","videoId":"8HkL25ulB2g","thumbnail":"https://img.youtube.com/vi/8HkL25ulB2g/hqdefault.jpg","category":"Entertainment","views":16,"likes":[],"dislikes":[],"createdAt":1778727529193,"_id":"QLVIGh52aUC5fc2r"}
