{"userId":"pADaTcDaTmqGephk","username":"d","title":" Wistoria: Wand and Sword - Episode 01 [English Sub]","description":"Will Serfort is a sixth-year student at Rigarden Magical Academy. He is known as a Learner, someone who excels only in theories. He cannot perform even the most basic spells and is looked down upon by his classmates as a flunkee. Despite this, he aims for the highest title of Magia Vander to fulfill a promise made to his childhood friend, Elfaria, although the path seems endlessly far. One day, while earning credits by defeating monsters in a dungeon as usual, Will encounters his classmates, including Sion, who scorn him. They are being attacked by a formidable enemy that should have been on the lower floors.","youtubeUrl":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uAS2RXlPsAk&list=PLwLSw1_eDZl3fj-ljtzKxYaTBgrqtcqoY","videoId":"uAS2RXlPsAk","thumbnail":"https://img.youtube.com/vi/uAS2RXlPsAk/hqdefault.jpg","category":"Entertainment","views":14,"likes":[],"dislikes":[],"createdAt":1778724954332,"_id":"yYAm4CkNzgMrRYgu"}
